<br>
I'm not advocating soloing as a way of life for a cleric, but I'm sure there are times for many of us when friends aren't around, or you're only on for a half hour or so, and you want to get a bit of experience.<br>
<br>
For me, I am available at odd hours and there aren't always friends or guildmates available to hunt with. There are a few places I've found to be good for soloing, but I was hoping to hear some more, perhaps bounce some ideas around.<br>
<br>
Right now, I do most of my soloing in Maiden's Eye, with my targets the Xi Xauis and Xi Vius. I buff myself up, get Koadic's if possible, and head to the corner near Akheva, usually. Magic resistance is *very* important for fighting here. My buffed MR is around 150.<br>
<br>
<br>
I go out scouting for a target. If it's a Xi Vius, I know it'll be a shadowknight. If it's a Xi Xaui, it's either a cleric or a shadowknight.. The only real difference is that with the clerics I make sure to sit and get a few stuns up for when they try to heal, and maybe sacrifice a damage over time for a nuke to knock them down a bit quicker.<br>
<br>
I usually pull by casting Epitaph of Life on the pet (if it's a shadowknight) or on the beast itself (if it's a cleric Xi Xaui, or the odd skeletal drudge that might show itself). Then I back up to a safer spot and cast Paralyzing Earth on the opponent, then stack my damage over time spells. <br>
<br>
With Epitaph of Life, Sermon of the Righteous, and Turning of the Unnatural, I'm doing 190 damage / tick, so I usually sit and med and recast the dots as necessary (and back up and recast root as necessary). I just keep doing that until it turns to flee, then I'll jump in with my hammer while continuing the dots. <br>
<br>
It works really well, and i find the experience in Maiden's Eye to be pretty much the best I can get on my own. I've tried other places,  like the Grey, but I find that they're a bit more annoying. Maiden's Eye is easy to get to, and easy to return to, should I get into trouble and need to gate.  Plus, there is always the chance for something nice off one of the Xis. Recently, I've recovered 2 shrouded medallions, a medallion of life, and today I got a shaded shield. Not amazing, but not bad for a cleric on her own.<br>
<br>
Do you have any other spots you'd like to share? Keep in mind, I'm only 56th season right now, so I don't have access to spells higher than this level. Any other secrets or ideas? <br>
<br>
Oh, and don't say anything like &quot;Why r u soloing? Go join a planes group!&quot; ... I don't like pick up groups.  Every once in a blue moon, pickup groups are good.. but more often than not, they're *bad*.<br>
