<br>
Clerics solo well in dungeons if the zone-in is safe.  Pick up a cheap Donal's Bracer for free pacify (level 55 cap).  Yes, you can eventually solo higher stuff (for fun I invised via potion down deep into the new droga and soloed a level 60 goblin there... a goblin cave lord or something like that) but most of the time, the bracer comes in handy for picking out singles.<br>
<br>
8th+ coldain rings, more damage shield.  That's something I really need to do.<br>
<br>
